snippet: Santonio Holmes had an injury scare, but X-rays on his chest came back negative, alleviating the Jets’ fears that he fractured a rib during a scrimmage in Cortland, N.Y.
abstract: New York Jets receiver Santonio Holmes has an injury scare during training camp, but X-rays on his chest come back negative, alleviating the fears that he fractured a rib; other NFL news noted.
lead_paragraph: Santonio Holmes had an injury scare, but X-rays on his chest came back negative, alleviating the Jets’ fears that he fractured a rib during a scrimmage in Cortland, N.Y.

headline.main: Sigh of Relief for the Jets
